snippet.title: Supergirl | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Look out. #Supergirl lands in theaters June 26.

‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô newest feature film to hit the big screen, will be in theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures, starring Milly Alcock in the dual role of Supergirl/Kara Zor-El.  Craig Gillespie directs the film from a screenplay by Ana Nogueira.

When an unexpected and ruthless adversary strikes too close to home, Kara Zor-El, aka Supergirl, reluctantly joins forces with an unlikely companion on an epic, interstellar journey of vengeance and justice.

Alcock stars alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and James Gunn are producing the film, which is based on characters from DC, Supergirl based on characters created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.  The film is executive produced by Nigel Gostelow, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars P. Winther.  Behind the camera, Gillespie is joined by director of photography Rob Hardy, production designer Neil Lamont, editor Tatiana S. Riegel, costume designer Anna B. Sheppard, Visual Effects Supervisor Geoffrey Baumann, and composer Ramin Djawadi.  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment Production, The Safran Company Production, A Film by Craig Gillespie, ‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ across North America on June 26, 2026, and internationally beginning 24 June 2026, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

Byah Ki Tyari (Official Video) Diler Kharkiya | Anjali Raghav | New Haryanvi Song 2025

#winterSong #newharyanvisong #newharyanvisongsharyanavi2025 #newharyanvisong2025 #hariyanvisong #haryanvi #haryanvisongs 

Song Credits :-

Singer / Composer - Diler Kharkiya
Starring - Diler Kharkiya , Anjali Raghav

Aaj happy happy laage se
Makha jo kuch se tere aage se 

Aaj happy happy laage se
Makha jo kuch se tere aage se 

Aaj badli badli dikhe se , teri kyaki tyari ho rii se
In jhadya ohoooo
In jhadya mai jaan meri 
Mere byah ki tyari ho rii se

Yo ke matter se smjha na mai
Kr rakhya confuse tne 
Sabte pehla tere aage share krii good news mne 

Rr ghrkya nai tohh rakhya se 
Ya aape kr liya choose tne 
Meri pasand ka se chhora 
Woh rakhega mahfooz mne 

Haye meri pasand ka se chhora woh rakhega mahfooz mne 

Tu paapan dil ki kali mere te 
Kadd ki baat lakko rii se
Ho in jhadya mein ohoo

Ho in jhadya mein jaan meri mere byah ki tyari ho rii se - 3

Rr kit ka se husband tera na bera pta thikaane ka 
Sahar Bhiwani suna to hoga khas jhila hariyane ka

Rr kisne chhora tohya se tu naam bta us syaane ka
Tu jaane mhare bichole ne woh babaji nindhane ka 
Haaye jaane mhare bichole ne woh babaji nindhane ka 

Diler Kharkiya bandhra mera jis gail chle love story se
Oh in jhadya mein ohoo

snippet.title: Anuv Jain - INAAM (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
The 15th studio recorded single - Inaam, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Listen to 'Inaam' on all streaming platforms : https://UMGI.lnk.to/Inaam_AnuvJain


Audio Credits: 

Artist: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Composer: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Producer: Lost Stories (@loststories)
Guitars: Keba Jeremiah (@kebajr)
Choirs: Solomon Konwar (@eskay______) Prachi Kapil (@prachi.kapil8)
Mix Engineers: Rishab Joshi (@rishabjoshi) & Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Master Engineer: Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Recording Engineer: Jay Rana (@itsjayrana)
Additional Programming: Sarthak Kalyani (@sarthak.kalyani)
Dolby Atmos Mastered at Ferris Wheel Studios (@ferriswheelstudios)

Video Credits: 

Director: Bhagyesh Rajeshirke (@bhagyesh_rajeshirke)
Associate Director: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Creative Director: Pranjal Asha (@pranjalasha)
Editor: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Producer: Arnab Kar (@arnab_kar)

Management: REPRESENT
Managers: Shirsodhi Banerjee (@shirsodhi), Kartik Iyer (@kartik_iyer_)

Inaam Lyrics: 

Paragraph 1

Malum 
Hai na 
Hum janay 
Tumko tumse zyada

Tumko 
Mila hai woh
Saalon se 
Jo bhi hai manga

Pre-chorus 1

Kaise khilono ki 
Ro ro ke
Karte the mangay 

Ik bar mil jaye 
Do din mein
Hi bhul jatay  

Chorus 1

Lekin khilono ke dil 
Toh hote hi nahin the

Dil toh humara hai 
Janay galat kya sahi yeh

Kitna the chahte par
Ab tumko yaad na aatey 
Hum

Paragraph 2

Kya yaad tumko 
Tum humko
‚ÄòInaam‚Äô the kehte 

Karte the kitna kuch
Panay ki chah 
Mein pehlay 


Pre-chorus 2

Ab yeh inaam ka 
Tum pe ilzaam hai jana

Dil hai gawah
Jeete jabse ho
Tumko hai hara 

Chorus 2

Cheezein badalti hain 
Itna toh hum ne bhi mana

Itna badal jaogay 
Jana kisne tha jana  

Jo tha parvana 
Ab usko humari parwah na 
Kyun?

Pre-Bridge

Dil mein baat kya hai?
Haan bolo humse 

Chahta aur kya hai? 
Haan bolo humse

Kya kami yahan hai?
Haan bolo humse na

Jo kaha mila hai
Haan bolo humse 

Badle mein bhala hai
Haan bolo humse

Manga tumse kya hai
Hai manga zara sa hi, kya hi, 

Kya? haye

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa

Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri

India's Focus

The 3rd T20l between India and South Africa is scheduled to be played today, December 14, 2025, at thehimachal pradesh Stadium in Dharamshala.
This match marks the start of a five-match T20l series, highly anticipated as it features the return of key Indian players and a promising new pitch at the venue.
India (IND)
‚Ä¢ Captaincy: India will be led by Suryakumar Yadav.
‚Ä¢ Key Returns: Both premier all-rounder Hardik Pandya and vice-captain Shubman Gill are back in the squad after recovering from injuries, which is a major boost for the team. Hardik Pandya has already shown good form in his return to competitive cricket.
‚Ä¢ Young Brigade: Following the retirements of senior players, india is continuing to back its younger players like Sanju Samson, Abhishek Sharma, and Tilak Varma in
‚Ä¢ Form: India has generally been in good T20l form, winning their recent series against Australia. They will be looking to continue that momentum at home.
South Africa (SA)
‚Ä¢ Captaincy: Aiden Markram is the captain for the Proteas in the T20l format.
‚Ä¢ Strong Squad: South Africa has named a full-strength squad, eager to challenge the world champions in their own conditions.
‚Ä¢ Players to Watch: Experienced T20 players like David Miller, Corbin Bosch and all-rounder Marco Jansen will be crucial in a bid to seek revenge for their T20 World Cup final loss.

snippet.title: KEN GAON JIMA SAJANI//Full VIDEO//Sambalpuri Video //Sana & Dibya// Singer-Priyadarshinee & Pratyush
snippet.description:
Welcome To Priya Vision YouTube Channel. Here You'll Find Hindi, Odia & Sambalpuri  Songs. Please Like, Share & Subscribe... 
this song is about the real life of a poor society and their situation who forces them to leave the beautiful motherland in search of food and shelter for their family. It also reflects how love exists in between them although they lack many sophisticated and luxurious things, the bond of family doesn't rely on luxury, happiness remains in togetherness and affection inbetween them. Gadgets are not the real needs, minimum needs are food, cloth and shelter which shouldn't be taken away from a society. Hope it will touch your hearts...Best wishes from Priya Vision
